Also in [[March 2007]] the ''Times'' faced rumors that publisher [[David Hiller]] suggested and approved former Secretary of Defense, [[Donald Rumsfeld]], with whom Hiller has close personal and business contacts, for a guest editorial position at the newspaper.<ref name="Rumsfeld and LA Times">
